product.longDescription: A true bibb with exceptional bolt tolerance. Uniform, dense heads are layered with crisp, semi-savoy leaves. Pairs beautifully with Cegolaine and Newham. Plant Variety Protected. High resistance to downy mildew races EU 16–26, 31, 32, US 5–9, Nasonovia ribisnigri aphid, and lettuce root aphid. MT0-30. Avg. 1,200 seeds/oz. Packet: 250 seeds.
